# React Components

- **Function components only** — no class components except `src/shared/components/error-boundary/ErrorBoundary.tsx`
- Props: define `interface <ComponentName>Props` — no inline object types for components with 3+ props
- Co-locate component-only types in the same file if not reused; move to `features/<name>/types/` when shared within the feature
- **Never** put business logic inside JSX — extract to hooks or plain functions above the component
- List rendering: always use a stable `key` (`id` field) — never array index unless the list is provably static and never reordered
- Keep components focused — split when a file exceeds ~150 lines or mixes data-fetching with heavy UI

## Imports

- Use `@/` alias for all internal imports
- Import shadcn primitives from `@/shared/components/ui/*`
